Function Microsoft Azure adapter and {{buildTool}} plugins offered by {{platform}}.

Check the documentation for detailed information on [using the Azure adapter](https://docs.spring.io/spring-cloud-function/reference/{{version}}/adapters/azure-intro.html) and [setting
up the {{buildTool}} build, along with a full build setup sample](https://docs.spring.io/spring-cloud-function/reference/{{version}}/adapters/azure-intro.html#azure.configuration).
